的他來說，體能測試是極大的挑戰，要10分半鐘內跑完2.4公里，亦要做掌上壓及仰臥起坐，首輪面試因跑步不達標而失敗。但他並沒有放棄，返港苦操3、4個月後再接受挑戰，2013年過關斬將通過所有測試，成功取錄。<br />\n<br />\n身為英皇室的御林軍，薪酬福利令人關注，David則不予透露，僅指薪金水平較香港警察低一些，除普通的醫療和交通福利外，最優厚是住房福利，他與同事在倫敦市中心合住一間800至900平方呎單位，月租只需30英鎊，僅相當於300港元，相信令不少香港青年人羨慕。<span style=\"color: red;\">他現長居英國，還有一年便可入籍</span>，目標是繼續在軍隊攀升，成爲終身職業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170812/bkn-20170812093047180-0812_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170812%2Fbkn-20170812093047180-0812_00822_001.html&d=ZB1ESaTuGoET0BYUrCG2VQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=86fa4b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170812/bkn-20170812093047180-0812_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\nBNO與其去做慈母　不如加入英軍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/422251/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/422251/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nBritish Army roles - <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apply.army.mod.uk/roles\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapply.army.mod.uk%2Froles&d=ZB1ESaTuGoET0BYUrCG2VQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1f9b94e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apply.army.mod.uk/roles</a>"},{"pid":"52f22fc5f3aa7aa1c77c9656ac7af38109eabfcd","tid":665074,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05aa166328eaa24802a012a68b8215ee67a6a68b","tid":665074,"uid":92937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0a5ebccbb2fed3e375ae1f18f6fd4a7a6ec894e","tid":665074,"uid":36844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d381b98571aa624032caa6a3867a3385f74c5c5","tid":665074,"uid":92937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"中學同學，大學同學一個都無咁慘慘豬？<br />\n鄰居呢？老師呢？有無返教會呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"佢話要係專業人士，我身邊有居英權同BNO嘅唔係專業人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\